definitions.definition: The national language of Cambodia , part of the Mon-Khmer language family.
An abugida used to write the Khmer language and sometimes Pali .

main_definition: The national language of Cambodia , part of the Mon-Khmer language family.
secondary_definitions: An abugida used to write the Khmer language and sometimes Pali .

definitions.definition: A member of an ethnolinguistic group that constitutes most of the population of Cambodia.
